      "rendered": "Sponsor the Open Data Project"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project/\"><strong>Open Data Project</strong></a> sponsorships are a unique opportunity to reach tens of thousands of nonprofit professionals worldwide. The cost to sponsor the Open Data Project for 12 months is $1,200.</p>\n<h4><strong>Benefits:</strong></h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Your logo and website are featured on all pages of the <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project/\">Open Data Project</a>.</li>\n<li>Your company/organization is featured in quarterly <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/category/open-data-project/\">blog posts</a> about the data.</li>\n<li>You have the option to write <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/publish-a-sponsored-blog-post/\">one sponsored post</a> (at no cost) using the data for Nonprofit Tech for Good.</li>\n<li>The ability to request exclusive configurations of the data.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>To learn more about becoming a sponsor for the Open Data Project, please\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/heather-mansfield/\">contact Heather Mansfield</a>.\u00a0</strong></p>\n<hr />\n<h2>Open Data Project Sponsors</h2>\n<div class=\"wptb-container-legacy\" data-table-id=\"28026\">\n    <table class=\"wptb-preview-table wptb-element-main-table_setting-28026\" data-reconstraction=\"1\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; border-image: initial;\" data-wptb-table-tds-sum-max-width=\"267\" data-wptb-cells-width-auto-count=\"1\" role=\"table\" data-table-columns=\"2\" data-wptb-header-background-color=\"\" data-wptb-even-row-background-color=\"\" data-wptb-odd-row-background-color=\"\" data-wptb-extra-styles=\"LyogRW50ZXIgeW91ciBjdXN0b20gQ1NTIHJ1bGVzIGhlcmUgKi8=\"><tbody><tr class=\"wptb-row\"><td class=\"wptb-cell\" style=\"border-width: 1px; width: 107px;\" data-x-index=\"0\" data-y-index=\"0\"><div class=\"wptb-image-container wptb-ph-element wptb-element-image-8 edit-active\" data-wptb-image-alignment=\"center\"><div class=\"wptb-image-wrapper\">            <a style=\"display: block;\" class=\"\" href=\"https://www.eventgroove.com/\" target=\"_blank\">                                <img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wptb-image-element-target\" height=\"44\" width=\"200\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Eventgroove-Logo.png?resize=200%2C44\" style=\"width: 100%;\">            </a>        </div></div></td><td class=\"wptb-cell\" style=\"border-width: 1px;\" data-x-index=\"1\" data-y-index=\"0\"><div class=\"wptb-text-container wptb-ph-element wptb-element-text-3\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 70, 69); font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"\" style=\"position: relative;\"><p><strong><a data-mce-href=\"https://www.eventgroove.com/\" href=\"https://www.eventgroove.com/\" style=\"color: rgb(30, 75, 176);\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Eventgroove</a></strong>&nbsp;is a one-stop platform for virtual, hybrid, and in-person events that offers event management, online fundraising, ticketing, and online storefronts for print and digital merchandise.</p></div></div></td></tr><tr class=\"wptb-row\" data-wptb-bg-color=\"\"><td class=\"wptb-cell\" data-y-index=\"1\" data-x-index=\"0\" style=\"border-width: 1px; width: 107px;\"><div class=\"wptb-image-container wptb-ph-element wptb-element-image-7\"><div class=\"wptb-image-wrapper\">            <a style=\"display: block;\" href=\"https://funraise.org/funraise-free\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/funraise-free.png?resize=200%2C88\" height=\"88\" width=\"200\" style=\"width: 100%;\"></a>        </div></div></td><td class=\"wptb-cell\" data-y-index=\"1\" data-x-index=\"1\" style=\"border-width: 1px;\" data-wptb-css-td-auto-width=\"true\"><div class=\"wptb-text-container wptb-ph-element wptb-element-text-1\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 70, 69); font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"\" style=\"position: relative;\"><p><a data-mce-href=\"https://funraise.org/funraise-free\" href=\"https://funraise.org/funraise-free\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(30, 75, 176);\"><strong>Funraise</strong></a>&nbsp;combines every fundraising tool that nonprofits need for success\u2014in one easy-to-use platform. Get started with free fundraising tools. Upgrade as you grow.</p></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n\n<hr />\n",
