    "excerpt": {
      "rendered": "<p>Open Data Project sponsorships are a unique opportunity to reach tens of thousands of nonprofit professionals worldwide. The cost to sponsor the Open Data Project for 12 months is $1,200. Benefits: Your logo and website are featured on all pages of the Open Data Project. Your company/organization is featured in quarterly blog posts about the data. You have the option to write one sponsored post (at no cost) using the data for Nonprofit Tech for Good. The ability to request exclusive configurations of the data. To learn more about becoming a sponsor for the Open Data Project, please\u00a0contact Heather Mansfield.\u00a0 </p>\n",
